Method Detail

setupConvenienceObjects

public void setupConvenienceObjects()
This method sets the convenience objects like newDefinition and oldDefinition, so you have short and easy handles to the new and old objects contained in the maintenance document. It also calls the BusinessObjectBase.refresh(), which will attempt to load all sub-objects from the DB by their primary keys, if available.
